                                 SK Shortcut Manager

                                                            

SK Shortcut Manager is designed for the quick and easy management of shortcuts (those in the Start Menu as well as in any other place).You can create, edit, delete, copy and move shortcuts. Apart from regular operations, you can associate any icons with shortcuts as well as with folders. You can also associate a shortcut with a hardware button.



                                      Features:



*show shortcuts in selected folder

*create shortcuts

*edit shortcuts

*change icon for shortcuts

*copy, move, rename, delete shortcut(s)

*assign shortcut to hardware button

*hide/unhide shortcuts

*create, rename, delete folder(s)

*change icon for folder

*QVGA, VGA support

*WM2003(SE), WM5 support

*English, German, Russian, Italian and Spanish UI language support
